<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A serious rush-hour crash on the M25 is causing eight-mile tailbacks at the Dartford crossing this morning.</p>

<p>The M25 is closed in both directions following the accident between junction five for the M26 and junction four for Orpington - adding hours to rush hour journeys this morning.</p>

<p>The road has been closed anti-clockwise since 5.25am while emergency services work at the scene.</p>

